12	FAQs		\N	<h1><strong>FAQs</strong></h1>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<h2><strong>Booking Tours</strong></h2>\n<ol style="list-style-type: lower-alpha;">\n<li>\n<h3><strong>How are tour guide services priced?</strong></h3>\nCanarini Tour Guides set the price based only on &ldquo;working hour-rate&rdquo; of tour guides. The fee will begin at the starting time when Tour guide meets you at your specific meeting point. The ending time is the time when Tour guide drops you drop off point. Handling fee &amp; customer services of 3% on the total amount will also be calculated.<br /><img src="/images/a3.png" /></li>\n<li>\n<h3><strong><strong>How do I book a tour guide?<br /></strong></strong></h3>\n<p><u>SINGLE BOOKING</u>: Need 1 TOUR GUIDE&nbsp; for 1 DAY TOUR - <a href="https://canarinitourguides.com/#/posts/2?current=13">Click here</a><u><br /></u></p>\n<p><u>MULTI - BOOKING</u>: -&nbsp;<u>Click here</u></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Need SEVERAL TOUR GUIDES for multi- group&nbsp; in 1 DAY&nbsp;</li>\n<li>Need SEVERAL TOUR GUIDES&nbsp; in multi-city&nbsp; in several days</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ol style="list-style-type: upper-alpha;">\n<li><u> SINGLE BOOKING</u><u></u></li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;<img src="/images/b2.png" /></p>\n<p><strong>Search the tour guides available on the tour destination and the date you want </strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;<img src="/images/c2.png" /></p>\n<p><strong>Select your tour guides </strong></p>\n<ul style="list-style-type: circle;">\n<li>Choose Tour Type, Language, Gender of Tour Guide.</li>\n<li>Click on the Tour Guide photos to read his/her profile.</li>\n<li>Click SELECT to choose your Tour Guide.</li>\n<li>Click CONTINUE to continue your booking.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Provide your booking&nbsp; information </strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>Time : </strong>\n<ul style="list-style-type: circle;">\n<li>Drag the bar to set your tour duration .</li>\n<li>The starting time is the time that Tour guide meet you at your specific meeting point.</li>\n<li>The ending time is the time that Tour guide drop you at the drop off point</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><strong>Location of&nbsp; Pick up &amp;&nbsp; Drop off&nbsp;</strong>\n<ul style="list-style-type: circle;">\n<li>Pick up &amp; Drop off services is availble for the city downtown area only. For the suburbs or other cities, you need to confirm with your Tour guide&nbsp; if He or She agrees&nbsp; with the terms and conditions agreed between You and Tour Guide only</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><strong>Traveller&rsquo;s information</strong>\n<ul style="list-style-type: circle;">\n<li><strong>Adult: </strong>the number of adult in your group ( including disable persons if applied )</li>\n<li><strong>Children:</strong> the number of children in your group ( including disable persons if applied )</li>\n<li><strong>Elder:</strong> the number of elder in your group ( including disable persons&nbsp; if applied )</li>\n<li><strong>Disable</strong>:\n<ul style="list-style-type: square;">\n<li>if you have any disable persons accompanied with you, please give the&nbsp; information of your requirements</li>\n<li>Tour Guide&nbsp; may&nbsp; refuse to serve your group if&nbsp; He/ or She was not advised about&nbsp; disable people in your group</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><strong>Primary guest information : </strong>\n<ul style="list-style-type: square;">\n<li>This is compulsory information. You should give the information of&nbsp; the representative&nbsp; guest who is attending the tour and act as the contact person on behalf of&nbsp; all group.</li>\n<li>The telephone number is the active telephone number that you can be reached. Our Tour guides will contact with you by the cellphone application such as viber, zalo so that you don&rsquo;t have to pay the roaming fee but be sure that you have the wi-fi available.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><strong>Other guest information:</strong> Although this is not compulsory information but we highly recommend that you should provide as much information as possible , at least you should provide one more representative guest information in case the primary guest can not be reached by telephone.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n<li>\n<h3><strong>My booking confirmation needs to be modified. What should I do? </strong></h3>\nFirstly, you need to register your account (hyperlink for Register), then sign in to Manage &nbsp;Your Account and Manage your booking. If you are already a registered User, Log In (hyperlink for Log In) to manage your booking and account.</li>\n<li>\n<h3><strong>The tour date that I want to book is marked &ldquo;unavailable&rdquo;. What should I do?</strong></h3>\nPlease choose another date you would like to start your tour / or Contact Us so we can help to look for an alternative Tour Guide for you.</li>\n<li>\n<h3><strong>Once my booking is confirmed by tour guide, how do I contact the guide?</strong></h3>\nOnce the booking is confirmed, you will be able to see your Tour Guide contact details where you can choose to call or send them a message.</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<ol start="2">\n<li>\n<h2><strong>General</strong></h2>\n<ol style="list-style-type: lower-alpha;">\n<li>\n<h3><strong>Can I phone the guide?</strong></h3>\nYES, You can. However, tour guide might be unable to receive the calls during their working hours, leave a message so they can contact you back as soon as possible.</li>\n<li>\n<h3><strong>After I have booked a tour guide, can I invite others to join me?<br /><img src="/images/d2.png" /><br /></strong></h3>\n</li>\n<li>\n<h3><strong>Who do I contact regarding the tour itinerary, pricing and/or guide availability?</strong></h3>\n<ul style="list-style-type: circle;">\n<li>Contact your Tour Guide directly in relation to any tour itinerary and related services.</li>\n<li>For tour guide availability, please contact us on our Customer Service.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<h3><strong>What should I do if my tour guide is not at the meeting location?</strong></h3>\n<ul style="list-style-type: circle;">\n<li><strong>STEP 1</strong>: Check your booking confirmation.<br /> <em>Are you at the correct meeting location?<br /> Are you on-time?<br /> Did you make alternate arrangements through email with the guide-partner that differs from the information posted on the booking confirmation?</em></li>\n<li><strong>STEP 2</strong>: If you are at the correct meeting location<sup>(*)</sup> at the appointed start time please call your tour guide FIRST on his/her mobile phone (<strong>see the booking confirmation for the phone number</strong>).</li>\n<li><strong>STEP 3</strong>: If you are unable to connect with your tour guide, please call our 24-hour traveller hotline (<strong>see the booking confirmation for the phone number</strong>).<br /><sup>(*)</sup><em>If the meeting location is at an airport or train station, please go to the Information Desk, your tour guide might be waiting for you there.</em></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<h3><strong>How does Canarini Tour Guides work?</strong></h3>\n</li>\n<li>\n<h3><strong>Do I need to tip my guide?</strong></h3>\nIt is recommended for a minimal of USD 5.00/per person/per day.</li>\n<li>\n<h3><strong>The tour guide hasn&rsquo;t replied to my inquiry. What should I do?</strong></h3>\n<ul style="list-style-type: circle;">\n<li>If after deposit, you can cancel the tour guide if you don&rsquo;t receive confirmation from selected tour guide, you might choose to cancel that tour guide and select another one OR get refund</li>\n<li>If after the tour guide confirmation, please send an email to our customer service, you can cancel the tour guide to select another one. Please prefer to the Cancellation Policy)</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<h3><strong>Do you work with travel agents?</strong></h3>\nYES we do. Please contact our Customer Service for package tours or any other special travel services.</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<ol start="3">\n<li>\n<h2><strong>Payment &amp; Refunds</strong></h2>\n<ol style="list-style-type: lower-alpha;">\n<li>\n<h3><strong>What kind of payment options do you offer?</strong></h3>\n<ul style="list-style-type: circle;">\n<li>We offer credit cards payment (VISA, AMEX, MasterCard) via Pay Pal.</li>\n<li>For our corporate clients, we offer payment via Wire transfer. Please contact Customer Service for detail about payment via wire transfer.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<h3><strong>What is your cancellation policy?<img src="/images/e.png" /><br /></strong></h3>\n</li>\n<li>\n<h3><strong>I may have accidentally paid for my tour MORE THAN ONCE. What should I do? </strong></h3>\nPlease contact our Customer Service for the refund.</li>\n<li>\n<h3><strong>Can I pay the tour guide in cash on the day of the tour?</strong></h3>\nUnless it&rsquo;s for admission fees or incidental costs such as meals, the option to pay the tour guide cash for the tour is not available.</li>\n<li>\n<h3><strong>How are exchange rates calculated?</strong></h3>\nAll the exchange rates are subject to your own banking institution.</li>\n<li>\n<h3><strong>Am I required to pay a deposit?</strong></h3>\nTo guarantee the legitimacy of the booking, a deposit is required.</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<ol start="4">\n<li>\n<h2><strong>Safety &amp; Security</strong></h2>\n<ol style="list-style-type: lower-alpha;">\n<li>\n<h3><strong>What can I do to ensure a safe and secure experience while on-tour</strong>?</h3>\nWe recommend that you purchase adequate medical and/or travel insurance prior to the tour date.\n<ul style="list-style-type: circle;">\n<li>Check out some of these useful tips while travelling abroad.</li>\n<li><u>Click Here </u>to view our Terms &amp; Conditions</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<h3><strong>What should I do if I feel unsafe during the tour?</strong></h3>\nYour safety and security is one of Canarini Tour Guides&rsquo;s priority concerns and so is your Tour Guide. If you feel unsafe:\n<ul style="list-style-type: circle;">\n<li>Communicate your concerns to your guide immediately</li>\n<li>You have the right to request your guide to stop the tour at any time. Your tour guide will have the obligation to return you to the agreed ending point by the transportation methods set out in the agreement/ description.</li>\n<li>Please report the incident immediately to Customer Support using the 24-hour emergency hotline number printed on your booking confirmation.</li>\n<li>Contact 911 in case of emergencies that require helps from the authority.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<ol start="5">\n<li>\n<h2><strong>Tour Guides</strong></h2>\n<ol style="list-style-type: lower-alpha;">\n<li>\n<h3><strong>How are your tour guides selected? <br /></strong></h3>\nBelow are the processing steps of how a tour guide list their services on our website: (tour guide sign up -&gt; submit their license -&gt; submit background check -&gt; get verified if eligible -&gt; account activation)</li>\n<li>\n<h3><strong>What kind of checks do you perform on your tour guides?</strong></h3>\nThe below processes will be conducted:\n<ul style="list-style-type: circle;">\n<li>Thorough reference and background checks. We subscribe to the redridgevs.com service and all applicants are screened through their database. All guides are re-screen every 6 months.</li>\n<li>Skills and knowledge of tour guides will be checked through relevant Certificate and via online test from our training program on Canarini Tour Guides website.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<h3><strong>What is the relationship between Canarini Tour Guides and the tour guides?<br /></strong></h3>\nCanarini Tour Guides and our registered tour guides have a mutual relationship and goal in providing you the best tour experience.\n<ul style="list-style-type: circle;">\n<li>Canarini Tour Guides provide a safe and secure online platform for Travelers to meet Local Tour Guides. We also ensure that both parties have a secure payment processing and customer supports in order to effectively deliver the best tour guiding services for our Clients.</li>\n<li>Our tour guides are independent contractors who will provide their expertise, knowledge and unique insights through the tours they create to best suit your interests.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<h3><strong>How do I know that a tour guide is competent?</strong></h3>\nOur tour guides are required to undergo a training program and frequent updates on the industry so that they fully understand their roles and responsibilities. We also provide you the information on uncensored Feedbacks and Ratings from previous travelers for each tour guides so you can have a better reference before choosing the tour guide that suits your travel plans most.<br /><u>After the deposit, you will be given your tour guide&rsquo;s contact detail to ask them any relevant questions about their experiences to make your decision.</u></li>\n<li>\n<h3><strong>How are tour guides paid?</strong></h3>\nTour Guides are paid Tuesday weekly for the tours they&rsquo;ve been booked the previous period. Payment is made electronically.</li>\n<li>\n<h3><strong>What if a guide is not available</strong>?</h3>\nCan I ask for a substitute? If your selected tour guide is not available, please have a look at the recommendations or contact our Customer Service so we can select a substitute for you as soon as possible.</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ol>	\N	\N	\N	on	1	2017-01-11 00:19:38.164556+00	2017-01-11 00:19:38.164556+00	29	0
