42	Your Booking Management		\N	<h1><strong>BOOK A TOUR GUIDE</strong></h1>\r\n<p>TRIPYAH GURU is an online platform to provide the&nbsp; Tour Guiding services only.</p>\r\n<p>How to book a Tour Guide - It&rsquo;s simple.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<h3>SINGLE BOOKING: Need 1 TOUR GUIDE&nbsp; for 1 DAY TOUR -&nbsp;<u>Click here</u></h3>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<h3>MULTI - BOOKING - <u>Click here</u>:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Need SEVERAL TOUR GUIDES for multi- group in 1 DAY</li>\r\n<li>Need SEVERAL TOUR GUIDES &nbsp;in multi-city&nbsp; in several days</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>A. SINGLE BOOKING</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><img src="/images/single_booking.png" /></strong></p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><strong>Step 1. Search the tour guides available on the tour destination and the date you want</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<img src="/images/SELECT.png" /></p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><strong>Step 2. Select&nbsp; your tour guides </strong></p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 60px;">&bull; Choose Tour Type, Language, Gender of Tour Guide</p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 60px;">&bull; Click on the Tour Guide photos to read his /her profile</p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 60px;">&bull; Click SELECT to choose your Tour Guide</p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 60px;">&bull; Click CONTINUE to continue your booking</p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><strong>Step 3. Provide your booking&nbsp; information </strong></p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><strong>a. Time : </strong></p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 90px;"> Drag the bar to set your tour duration.</p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 90px;"> The starting time is the time that Tour guide meet you at your specific meeting point.</p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 90px;"> The ending time is the time that Tour guide drop you at the drop off point.</p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 90px;"> A working day of Tour Guide&nbsp; is 08 hours . The extra working hour is subjected to a surcharge as below:</p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 60px;">&nbsp;<img src="/images/extra_hour.png" /></p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><strong>b. Location of&nbsp; Pick up &amp;&nbsp; Drop off&nbsp; </strong></p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 60px;">Pick up &amp; Drop off services is availble for the city downtown area only. For the suburbs or other cities, you need to confirm with your Tour guide &nbsp;if He or She agrees&nbsp; with the terms and conditions agreed between You and Tour Guide only.</p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><strong>c. Traveller&rsquo;s information </strong></p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 90px;"><strong> Adult: </strong>the number of adult in your group (including disable persons if applied)</p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 90px;"><strong> Children:</strong> the number of children in your group (including disable persons if applied)</p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 90px;"><strong> Elder:</strong> the number of elder in your group (including disable persons if applied)</p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 90px;"><strong> Disable</strong>:</p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 120px;"> if you have any disable persons accompanied with you, please give the&nbsp; information of your requirements</p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 120px;"> Tour Guide &nbsp;may &nbsp;refuse to serve your group if&nbsp; He/ or She was not advised about&nbsp; disable people in your group</p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 90px;"><strong> Primary guest information: </strong></p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 120px;"> This is compulsory information. You should give the information of&nbsp; the representative guest who is attending the tour and act as the contact person on behalf of all group.</p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 120px;"> The telephone number is the active telephone number that you can be reached . Our Tour guides will contact with you by the cellphone application such as viber, zalo so that you don&rsquo;t have to pay the roaming fee but be sure that you have the wi-fi available.</p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 90px;"><strong> Other guest information:</strong> Although this is not compulsory information but we highly recommend that you should provide as much information as possible , at least you should provide one more representative guest information in case the primary guest can not be reached by telephone</p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><strong>Step 4. Deposit </strong></p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><strong> </strong>You are requested to read the Terms and Conditions before your payment.</p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><strong> </strong>Choose the type of your credit card that you use to pay</p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><strong> </strong>Pay online</p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><strong>Step 5.&nbsp;Get confirmation of your&nbsp; selected tour guide</strong></p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><strong> </strong>After receiving your booking, Your selected tour guide will send a confirmation&nbsp; to you within 24 hours.</p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><strong> </strong>The selected tour guide confirm your booking, then a confirmation&nbsp; will be sent to your email with tour guide contact information.</p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><strong>Step 6.&nbsp;</strong><strong>Contact by email, phone call, chat with your selected tour guide</strong></p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><strong> </strong>You can contact&nbsp; and discuss with your tour guide about all requirements about your tour.</p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><strong> </strong><strong>NOTE:</strong></p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 90px;"> Tour Guides presented on the Site are independent contractors and third party providers of Canarini. Tour Guides are not employees or agents of Canarini. Therefore, Canarini does not control the quality, timing, legality, or any other aspect whatsoever of the services actually delivered by the Tour Guides. We use our best efforts to monitor the transactions conducted through our Services and aim to become a valuable resource to our users