ng coastline sceneries! The Blue Line shows off Oahu's southeastern coastline and highlights magnificent views of white sand beaches, dramatic cliffs and - if you&rsquo;re lucky - perhaps whales and dolphins. Featured Blue Line stops include: DFS Galleria Waikiki, Duke Kahanamoku Statue, Hanauma Bay, Halona Blow Hole, Sandy Beach, Sea Life Park, and Hawaii Kai Lookout.</li>\n</ul>	maxresdefault.jpg	\N	\N	on	1	2017-03-17 03:32:14.621733+00	2017-03-17 03:32:14.621733+00	58	5
